            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">COURSES</h5>
                <p class="card-text">There are almost <%=cc%> courses
                    that are very helpful with their content.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="public/lecture.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">LECTURES</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Almost <%=lc%> quick example text to build on mental strength and make up the bulk
                    of the brain's content.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
